<subSubSection id="FA2DB8A182B6DCCFB5D658D2F511A2CD" pageId="0" pageNumber="95" type="literature records">
<paragraph id="66CC0F4EA7269827C1A32DEDD467CA1F" pageId="0" pageNumber="95">Literature records.</paragraph>
<paragraph id="809F4838CAB02A9D7EF5F654B00727BE" pageId="0" pageNumber="95">
Malaysia. Kuala Lumpur, Pahang, Pangkor Island, Penang, Perak, Selangor (
<bibRefCitation id="B0ADF0287E090E0D1898F2D311052093" DOI="https://doi.org/10.3897/zookeys.101.1182" author="Engel, MS" journalOrPublisher="ZooKeys" pageId="0" pageNumber="95" pagination="51 - 80" refId="B20" refString="Engel, MS, Gonzalez, VH, 2011. Alocanthedon, a new subgenus of Chalicodoma from Southeast Asia (Hymenoptera, Megachilidae). ZooKeys 101: 51 - 80, DOI: https://doi.org/10.3897/zookeys.101.1182" title="Alocanthedon, a new subgenus of Chalicodoma from Southeast Asia (Hymenoptera, Megachilidae)." url="https://doi.org/10.3897/zookeys.101.1182" volume="101" year="2011">Engel and Gonzalez 2011</bibRefCitation>
). A photograph on iNaturalist from Buachet, Surin Province may pertain to this species but visual identification in this group is difficult (credit: janescan 2018).
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
