<subSubSection id="6E4FE5DDF7F4B7DCBCF9C0A235465709" pageId="0" pageNumber="95" type="remarks">
<paragraph id="659E9067633108805ACA4295610273E0" pageId="0" pageNumber="95">Remarks.</paragraph>
<paragraph id="4D6FD0B6B2D091813F239227FD129E37" pageId="0" pageNumber="95">This species was described from Peninsular Malaysia. It is remarkable that the first and only Thai specimen record is from Phayao Province in northern Thailand.</paragraph>
